'''Cartridge paper''' is a high quality type of heavy [[paper]] used for [[illustration]] and [[drawing]]. Paper of this type was originally used for making [[paper cartridge]]s for firearms.<ref>[http://cool.conservation-us.org/don/dt/dt0594.html A Dictionary of Descriptive Terminology: cartridge paper] (accessed 23 Oct 2009)</ref>
